    "body": "I see, nice find.\r\n\r\nthe issue here is that the `block` is ignored here:\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/foundry-rs/foundry/blob/67ab8704476d55e47545cf6217e236553c427a80/crates/cast/bin/cmd/call.rs#L185-L185\r\n\r\nbecause we expect `fork_block_number`.\r\n\r\nto fix this we can do:\r\n\r\n1. if BlockId is a not a number, get a provider:  `let provider = utils::get_provider(&config)?;` and convert the blockId to the number, then set it to evm_opts\r\n\r\nwe like need to convert the figment to the Config, see also:\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/foundry-rs/foundry/blob/67ab8704476d55e47545cf6217e236553c427a80/crates/config/src/lib.rs#L480-L482",
